---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SectionTitle from "../components/common/SectionTitle.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="上传文件 | VANMEE 凡觅" description="上传 STEP、STL、PDF 文件，获取工程评估。">
  <section class="section"><div class="container"><SectionTitle kicker="Upload" title="上传文件" subtitle="支持 STEP、STL、PDF 与需求说明。用于进入工程预评估。" /><div class="content-grid"><div class="panel" style="padding:24px;"><form class="form"><div class="field"><label>文件上传</label><input class="input" type="file" /></div><div class="field"><label>项目类型</label><select class="select"><option>验证模型</option><option>结构件</option><option>装配件</option><option>试制项目</option></select></div><div class="field"><label>简要描述</label><textarea class="textarea" placeholder="材料、数量、交期、精度、装配、表面要求..."></textarea></div><div class="btn-row"><button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">提交预评估</button><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/quote">进入报价页</a></div></form></div><div class="panel" style="padding:24px;"><div class="pill">Upload Rules</div><ul class="list-check" style="margin-top:14px;"><li>建议优先上传 STEP / STL</li><li>如有图纸，请附 PDF</li><li>说明验证目标有助于更快判断路径</li><li>复杂项目建议补充装配关系与数量</li></ul></div></div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
